<p class="">These provisions, so far as the undertakings which the Indian Government have given are concerned, and which have been stated to the House, cover the finance for these undertakings They do not, extend any undertaking made by the Indian Government, but provide the sterling for it.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
